high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the oval counter
Pick up the knife on the counter
Turn right, walk towards the sink
Place the knife in the sink, turn on the faucet to fill the sink with water, turn off the faucet, and retrieve the knife from the sink
Turn right and face the stove
Open the top drawer to the right of the oven and place the knife in. Close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Find and clean a knife before placing it in a drawer

high_descs: Turn left to head across the kitchen,take the yellow knife from the counter
Turn to the right, head to the sink, Put the yellow knife in the sink
Turn on the water for 4 seconds, take the knife out of the sink
Turn to the right, open the drawer next to the fridge,
put the knife in the drawer
Close the drawer next to the sink
anns.task_desc: Wash the yellow knife, put it in the drawer next to the fridge

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the large knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right and walk forward to the sink.
Put the knife in the sink, rinse it off, and take it back out of the sink.
Turn right towards the stove top.
Put the knife in the top drawer to the right of the stove top, then close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned knife in a drawer.
